window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Amber Bay, Alaska, has it all.</p> <p>A cozy log cabin with a roaring fireplace? Check.</p> <p>A remote location where my family can't find me? Check.</p> <p>Three hot guys I can't stop thinking about? Also check.</p> <p>But the small off-grid town also has a mysterious undercurrent running through it. People are wary of strangers—even though they don't know I'm a witch-and mothers shoo their children away when I'm near.</p> <p>Something's not right here, and I intend to find out what it is.</p> <p>But I'm afraid that digging up this town's secrets might expose my own.</p>"; 
